OL,3,GOPINIONCITV 70 coverage oversimplifying
OL,4,Cthe channel's past
OL,5,
OL,6,FSometimes the story of the present is
OL,7,Flost in the misrepresentation or
OL,8,Fmisunderstanding of the past.
OL,10,FThis is the case with some of the
OL,11,Fcoverage of ITV's 70th anniversary.
OL,13,FIt is too easy to distort the channel's
OL,14,Fstory by oversimplification and present
OL,15,Fthe past 70 years as one simple
OL,16,Fjourney.
OL,18,FThis matters.
OL,20,FHistory in all its forms can simply
OL,21,Fbecome the story of the victorious.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
