OL,3,GOPINIONCITV 70 coverage oversimplifying
OL,4,Cthe channel's past
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe story of ITV plc or of modern ITV 1
OL,7,Fis not the story of Independent
OL,8,FTelevision itself.
OL,10,FSadly, this has led to some confusing
OL,11,Fcoverage of the anniversary.
OL,13,FITV plc can trace its history back to
OL,14,FGranada Television and nobody should
OL,15,Fever understate Granada's achievements
OL,16,Fas a broadcaster.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
