OL,6,GCONDENSED HISTORY OF ITV
OL,8,FCommercial television in Britain is 70
OL,9,Fyears old.
OL,11,FThe first two commercial broadcasters
OL,12,Fin the UK ` Associated Rediffusion and
OL,13,FATV ` started broadcasting in the
OL,14,FLondon area in September 1955. Neither
OL,15,Fare still in business.
OL,17,FOver the next seven years, other
OL,18,Fcompanies began broadcasting across
OL,19,Fmost of the rest of the country.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
