OL,3,GOPINIONCITV 70 coverage oversimplifying
OL,4,Cthe channel's past
OL,5,
OL,6,FThese companies were all fiercely
OL,7,Findependent of each other ` serving
OL,8,Ftheir local areas while also acting
OL,9,Ftogether as a network.
OL,11,FThe regional map was redrawn
OL,12,Fsignificantly in 1968 and further
OL,13,Fmodified as a result of the switch to
OL,14,FUHF transmission.
OL,16,FBut, more significantly, many companies
OL,17,Fchanged over the years through
OL,18,Ffranchise rounds run by the regulator.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
