OL,3,GOPINIONCITV 70 coverage oversimplifying
OL,4,Cthe channel's past
OL,5,
OL,6,FAfter 1993, the regional companies
OL,7,Fstarted to merge with each other.
OL,8,FEventually one company owned all the
OL,9,Flicences outside Scotland.
OL,11,FToday ITV plc runs a national channel
OL,12,Fcalled ITV 1. But the service includes
OL,13,Fregional news and advertising plus some
OL,14,Fbespoke programmes for Wales and
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,17,FSome regional companies came and went
OL,18,Fin the franchise rounds ` some survived
OL,19,Fand have their legacy within ITV plc.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
